data.description: Charming Rancher with gleaming hardwood floors in the living room and 3 bedrooms.  Kitchen has new high end 42" cabinets, new stove and microwave, and new tile.  Home has new insulation, and new drywall, and new paint.  Large Family Room for Family gatherings.   Home has newer vinyl windows throughout.  Bathrooms have new vanities and tile and the shower has new tile surround.  Backyard has an oversized Patio that is shaded by a beautiful maple tree along with a storage shed and another utility building. Home has central air conditioning! New roof installed the 2nd week of November including the shed.
